# ── Tauri Updater 签名密钥（发布必需）──
# 生成命令: pnpm tauri signer generate
# 将公钥设为 GitHub Secret: DEVICEDECK_TAURI_UPDATER_PUBLIC_KEY
# 将私钥设为 GitHub Secret: DEVICEDECK_TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY
# 将密码设为 GitHub Secret: DEVICEDECK_TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PASSWORD

# DEVICEDECK_TAURI_UPDATER_PUBLIC_KEY=
# DEVICEDECK_TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY=
# DEVICEDECK_TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PASSWORD=

# ── 发布流程 ──
# 1. 更新 CHANGELOG.md
# 2. pnpm bump x.y.z
# 3. git commit -am "chore: release x.y.z"
# 4. git tag vx.y.z
# 5. git push origin vx.y.z
# GitHub Actions 自动构建并发布
